org.jhove2.module.display.util
Class ContainerMDWrapper

java.lang.Object
  org.jhove2.module.display.util.ContainerMDWrapper

public final class ContainerMDWrapper
extends Object

A wrapper for the data needed to build the containerMD section of the manifest. Data are gathered during the parse of the JHove2 characterization result analysis and aggregated.
